                        <decoDesc>
                            <summary>An initial folio features the illuminated opening, while
                                twenty-six illustrations feature the following scenes:</summary>
                            <decoNote type="headpiece">A detached illuminated opening of the work
                                features a domed scalloped mandorla surmounted by a detached gold
                                medallion, with split cloud-collar motifs between at right at left,
                                with a blank horizontal gilt cartouche with within a rectangle
                                below, infilled floral scrollwork set against an ultramarine
                                ground.</decoNote>
